00:55:41,516 --> 00:55:47,739
Well my opinion. That's a great question by the way my opinion is I think we should be transparent because I think

818
00:55:48,940 --> 00:55:49,580
if players

819
00:55:50,413 --> 00:55:55,777
hear about the exploit from you, it's much better than the potential of them hearing about it from

